    <title>Changing the MTU on a small-footprint System</title>
    <shortdesc>
        <draft-comment author="rstone">Topic created for CGTS-1944</draft-comment>
    </shortdesc>
    <prolog><author/>
     
    </prolog>
    <body>
        
            <p>The following steps illustrate how to change the MTU for an interface
                for an infrastructure network. </p>
        
        <ol>
             
                <li>Lock Controller-1.
                 <ol>
                    
                        <li>From 
                            <b>System</b>, then
                            <b>Instances</b>, then
                         select the <b>Hosts</b> tab.</li>
                    
                    
                        <li>From the <b>Edit</b> menu for Controller-1, select
                            <b>Lock Host</b>.
                        
                            
                                <image href="rst1442611298701.image"/>
                            
                        </li>
                    
                 </ol>
                </li>
             
                <li>Modify the MTU of an interface on controller-1.
                 <ol>
                    
                        <li>Click on the name of controller-1, then switch to the
                                <b>Interfaces</b> tab and select
                                <b>Edit</b> for the interface you want to
                            change.</li>
                    
                    
                        <li>In the <b>Edit Interface</b> dialog, change the
                                <b>MTU</b> field, then click
                                <b>Save</b>. </li>
                    
                </ol>
                </li>
             
                <li>Unlock Controller-1.
                
                    <p>From the <b>Edit</b> menu for Controller-1, select
                        <b>Unlock Host</b>.</p>
                
                </li>
             
                <li>Swact host to Controller-1
                
                    
                        <image href="psa1420751608971.image"/>
                    
                </li>
            
             
                <li>Lock controller-0</li>
            
             
                <li>Modify the MTU of an interface on controller-0</li>
            
             
                <li>Unlock Controller-0</li>
            
        </ol>
    </body>
